    <bodyTop>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>The programme’s aim is to produce reflective graduates who have a broad understanding of the practice, history and theory of film, journalism and media studies, students who are informed by knowledge of the conventions and influences of a variety of genres and production styles. This programme is suitable for professionals of the Media market interested in enhancing their academic background, and gives the opportunity of advance entry to professionals and graduates with Institute of Vocational Training (IVT) Diplomas.</p>]]></Value>
    </bodyTop>
