    "content": "<p>Titles :</p>\n<ul>\n<li>BA in Media Production: Film Directing</li>\n<li>BA in Media Production: Journalism</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://scqf.org.uk/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Scottish Credit and Qualifications Framework\">SCQF Level</a> : 9</p>\n<p>Mode of delivery :  Face-to-face, full-time</p>\n<p>Duration : normally 3 years</p>\n<p>Language of delivery : Greek</p>"
  },
